src:
Nina niže pobede
07 Nov 2019, 14:31 by Milos
Nina Stojanović izborila je plasman u četvrtfinale WTA čelendžera u Šemženu, koji se igra za nagradni fond od 100 hiljada dolara.
Najbolja srpska teniserka je na turniru u Kini porazila domaću pšredstavnicu Čang Liu sa 2:0, po setovima 6:1, 6:4, nakon jednog časa i četiri minuta igre. Nina će se za plasman u polufinale boriti sa Jasmin Paolini iz Italije.
Druga srpska predstavnica na turniru u Šenženu, Natalija Kostić, poražena je u osmini finala od Japanke Kurumi Nare sa 2:0 (6:2, 6:4).

POVEZANE OBJAVE
text:
Nina's lower wins
07 Nov 2019, 14:31 by Milos
Nina Stojanovic has won the quarterfinals of the WTA Shemzeng, which is being played for a $ 100,000 prize pool.
The best Serbian tennis player defeated home team changer Chang Liu in the tournament in China 2-0, by sets 6: 1, 6: 4, after one hour and four minutes of play. Nina will compete with Jasmin Paolini of Italy for the semifinals.
The other Serbian representative in the Shenzhen tournament, Natalija Kostic, was defeated in the eighth finals by Japan's Kurumi Nara 2-0 (6: 2, 6: 4).
